dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Burnett Peak quadrangle, San Luis Obispo and Monterey counties, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle, Burnett Peak CA 1949. AMS 1755 I SW, series V895."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology, most recent 1970.
